    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nFind the sum of the interior angles of a polygon with 8 sides.\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\nSum of interior angles of an n-sided polygon = (n\u22122) \u00d7 180\u2218 \nSum = (8 \u2212 2) \u00d7 180 = 6 \u00d7 180 = 1080\u2218",
